                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Resize:</Run> Drag the chart height thumb to adjust each chart's size.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Detach:</Run> Pop a chart into its own floating window for multi-monitor use.<LineBreak/>
