                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Histogram:</Run> Statistical distribution of registration values.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Revolutions:</Run> Revolution type analysis (One Only, First of Many, Last of Many).<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Missing Data:</Run> Identifies gaps and missing data points.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Skew:</Run> Skew analysis across stations.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Skew Along Bracket:</Run> Skew analysis along the bracket direction.
                    </TextBlock>

                    <TextBlock Text="Filters &amp; Options" Style="{StaticResource SubHeaderStyle}"/>
