                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Revolution:</Run> Filter by revolution type.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Iteration:</Run> Select specific iteration number.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Cycle Range:</Run> Set from/to cycle range.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Column Range:</Run> Set from/to column range.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Remove DC:</Run> Remove DC offset from signals.<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Auto Y Axis:</Run> Automatically scale Y axis (or set manual range).<LineBreak/>
                        ‚Ä¢ <Run>Smoothing:</Run> Apply signal smoothing.<LineBreak/>
